sequenceDiagram
    participant Client
    participant Gateway as Istio Gateway
    participant MLflow as MLflow Server
    participant K8S as Kubernetes API
    participant PG as PostgreSQL
    participant S3 as S3 Storage

    Note over Client,S3: Flow 1: Experiment Tracking
    Client->>Gateway: POST /api/2.0/mlflow/runs/create (443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.2+)
    Gateway->>MLflow: Forward request (5000/TCP HTTP Bearer Token)
    MLflow->>K8S: SubjectAccessReview (6443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.2+)
    K8S-->>MLflow: Authorized
    MLflow->>PG: INSERT run metadata (5432/TCP PostgreSQL TLS 1.2+ opt)
    PG-->>MLflow: Run ID
    MLflow-->>Gateway: 201 Created with run_id
    Gateway-->>Client: 201 Created

    Client->>Gateway: POST /api/2.0/mlflow/runs/log-metric (443/TCP HTTPS)
    Gateway->>MLflow: Forward request (5000/TCP HTTP Bearer Token)
    MLflow->>K8S: SubjectAccessReview (6443/TCP HTTPS)
    K8S-->>MLflow: Authorized
    MLflow->>PG: INSERT metric (5432/TCP PostgreSQL)
    PG-->>MLflow: Success
    MLflow-->>Client: 200 OK

    Note over Client,S3: Flow 2: Artifact Upload
    Client->>Gateway: PUT /api/2.0/mlflow-artifacts/artifacts (443/TCP HTTPS)
    Gateway->>MLflow: Forward artifact (5000/TCP HTTP Bearer Token)
    MLflow->>K8S: SubjectAccessReview (6443/TCP HTTPS)
    K8S-->>MLflow: Authorized
    MLflow->>K8S: Check MLflowConfig for namespace artifact override (6443/TCP HTTPS)
    K8S-->>MLflow: Artifact config (bucket path)
    MLflow->>S3: PUT object (443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.2+ AWS IAM)
    S3-->>MLflow: Success
    MLflow->>PG: UPDATE artifact path (5432/TCP PostgreSQL)
    MLflow-->>Client: 200 OK

    Note over Client,S3: Flow 3: Model Registration
    Client->>Gateway: POST /api/2.0/mlflow/registered-models/create (443/TCP HTTPS)
    Gateway->>MLflow: Forward request (5000/TCP HTTP Bearer Token)
    MLflow->>K8S: SubjectAccessReview (6443/TCP HTTPS)
    K8S-->>MLflow: Authorized (registeredmodels create)
    MLflow->>PG: INSERT registered model (5432/TCP PostgreSQL)
    PG-->>MLflow: Model ID
    MLflow-->>Client: 201 Created

    Note over Client,PG: Flow 4: LLM Trace Ingestion
    Client->>Gateway: POST /api/3.0/mlflow/traces (443/TCP HTTPS)
    Gateway->>MLflow: Forward trace (5000/TCP HTTP Bearer Token)
    MLflow->>K8S: SubjectAccessReview (6443/TCP HTTPS)
    K8S-->>MLflow: Authorized
    MLflow->>S3: Store trace data (443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.2+)
    S3-->>MLflow: Success
    MLflow->>PG: INSERT trace metadata (5432/TCP PostgreSQL)
    MLflow-->>Client: 201 Created
